{"title":"New Terraform Tutorial: Sensitive Input Variables","link":"https://www.hashicorp.com/blog/terraform-sensitive-input-variables","date":1609963200000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><section><p>HashiCorp Terraform configuration often includes sensitive inputs, such as passwords, API tokens, or Personally Identifiable Information (PII). Terraform provides several features to help avoid accidentally exposing sensitive data.</p><h2>Learn to Protect Sensitive Inputs</h2><p><span>Follow our new tutorial on HashiCorp Learn, </span><a href=\"https://learn.hashicorp.com/tutorials/terraform/sensitive-variables?in=terraform/configuration-language&amp;utm_source=WEBSITE&amp;utm_medium=WEB_BLOG&amp;utm_offer=ARTICLE_PAGE\"><span>Protect Sensitive Input Variables</span></a><span>. In this tutorial, you will provision a web application using Terraform, and use the `sensitive` variable flag to set sensitive values. You will also learn about ways to manage sensitive values in your Terraform state.</span></p><h2>Use the “sensitive” Flag</h2><p><span>New in Terraform 0.14, input variables now support the `sensitive` flag. Terraform will redact the values of sensitive variables in console and log output, to reduce the risk of accidentally disclosing these values.</span></p></section><section><picture data-testid=\"image-root\"><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960116-tf-input-1.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=250 250w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960116-tf-input-1.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=500 500w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960116-tf-input-1.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=750 750w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960116-tf-input-1.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=1000 1000w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960116-tf-input-1.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=1500 1500w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960116-tf-input-1.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=2000 2000w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960116-tf-input-1.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=2500 2500w\" sizes=\"100vw\" data-testid=\"webp-source\"><img src=\"https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960116-tf-input-1.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80\" srcset=\"https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960116-tf-input-1.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=250 250w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960116-tf-input-1.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=500 500w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960116-tf-input-1.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=750 750w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960116-tf-input-1.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=1000 1000w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960116-tf-input-1.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=1500 1500w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960116-tf-input-1.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=2000 2000w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960116-tf-input-1.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=2500 2500w\" sizes=\"100vw\" alt=\"Code block defining variable &quot;db_password&quot;\" data-testid=\"img\"></picture></section><section><p><span>When you apply this configuration, Terraform redacts the sensitive value from its console output.</span></p></section><section><picture data-testid=\"image-root\"><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960199-tf-input-2.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=250 250w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960199-tf-input-2.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=500 500w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960199-tf-input-2.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=750 750w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960199-tf-input-2.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=1000 1000w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960199-tf-input-2.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=1500 1500w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960199-tf-input-2.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=2000 2000w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960199-tf-input-2.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=2500 2500w\" sizes=\"100vw\" data-testid=\"webp-source\"><img src=\"https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960199-tf-input-2.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80\" srcset=\"https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960199-tf-input-2.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=250 250w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960199-tf-input-2.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=500 500w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960199-tf-input-2.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=750 750w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960199-tf-input-2.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=1000 1000w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960199-tf-input-2.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=1500 1500w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960199-tf-input-2.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=2000 2000w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960199-tf-input-2.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=2500 2500w\" sizes=\"100vw\" alt=\"Code block running `terraform apply`. Output shows warnining that attribute value will be marked as sensitive and will not display in UI output.\" data-testid=\"img\"></picture></section><section><p><span>This feature helps prevent accidental disclosure of sensitive values, but is not sufficient to fully secure your Terraform configuration.</span></p><h2>Secure Terraform State</h2><p><span>Even when a variable is marked sensitive, Terraform still needs to store the value in its state file, so that it can correctly apply configuration changes.</span></p></section><section><picture data-testid=\"image-root\"><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960313-tf-inputs-3.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=250 250w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960313-tf-inputs-3.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=500 500w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960313-tf-inputs-3.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=750 750w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960313-tf-inputs-3.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=1000 1000w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960313-tf-inputs-3.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=1500 1500w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960313-tf-inputs-3.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=2000 2000w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960313-tf-inputs-3.png?fit=max&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=80&amp;w=2500 2500w\" sizes=\"100vw\" data-testid=\"webp-source\"><img src=\"https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960313-tf-inputs-3.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80\" srcset=\"https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960313-tf-inputs-3.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=250 250w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960313-tf-inputs-3.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=500 500w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960313-tf-inputs-3.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=750 750w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960313-tf-inputs-3.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=1000 1000w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960313-tf-inputs-3.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=1500 1500w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960313-tf-inputs-3.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=2000 2000w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1609960313-tf-inputs-3.png?fit=max&amp;fm=png&amp;q=80&amp;w=2500 2500w\" sizes=\"100vw\" alt=\"Code block running `grep &quot;password&quot; terraform.tfstate`\" data-testid=\"img\"></picture></section><section><p><span>In this tutorial, you will learn about several methods that Terraform and other HashiCorp products provide to secure your state file.</span></p><p><span>Read: </span><a href=\"https://learn.hashicorp.com/tutorials/terraform/sensitive-variables?in=terraform/configuration-language&amp;utm_source=WEBSITE&amp;utm_medium=WEB_BLOG&amp;utm_offer=ARTICLE_PAGE\"><span>Protect Sensitive Input Variables</span></a></p></section></div></div>","author":"Robin Norwood","siteTitle":"HashiCorp Blog","siteHash":"219aa6310b3388f2335eba49871f4df9581f2c58eaeb5e498363b54e835b7001","entryHash":"79b85dd97dadb6d8139970600e1d5813f5a53bdc5f0546632935125430381722","category":"Tech"}